  "formulaSource": "Block count calculations based on National Concrete Masonry Association (NCMA) TEK 4-1A — Productivity and Modular Coordination in Concrete Masonry Construction. Effective face area includes mortar joint added to length and height of each block. Mortar estimate of 3.5 bags (80 lb) per 100 blocks based on NCMA TEK 3-8A standard for 3/8\" joints. Fill concrete at 0.8 cu ft per standard 8\" CMU core.",
